channel.title: I finally got a question I cant answer XD
channel.description: Ok well as you know I own hiyascape server and I run it off my dads computer which has a router for my brothers ps3 and I port forwarded the router and im sad because people can't get on my server at my moms house because she has DSL and im at her house most of the time, so when I go to my default it shows me no port forwarding,and as I heard some people said you don't have to port forward with dsl so I just trusted them and downloaded my source so then I compile and run it and no one can get on so I went in DUC and clicked boxes and let those work so it updated and then I opened my port through my modem and no one can get on still and I can log on the 0.0.0.0 and the 127.0.0.1 and play but no one can get on help please ;)
